rComments: She teaches the very basics in lecture, but the homework problems she assigns are far more difficult. Yet those are the ones that show up on tests. She's not very helpful and assumes everyone already has a strong physics background. Her lectures slides are disorganized with many diagrams and equations crammed onto the slide. Avoid at all costs.
